{
  "stem": "5388.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I testified to it in the court afterward.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Visa ?] was the head of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I go outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They push me through the window.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a church.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I go through, and--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CLAPS] I'm outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I go to, to Tadek.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And lo and behold, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Arrangements were made.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mind my own business.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So now I have to give the message the [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Lisa ?] and Aaron.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One half of the ghetto was on one side of the street, was the Jewish ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was already a small one, on some [? covered ?] street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "On the other side, outside of the ghetto, was-- the other side of the street was the Aryan side, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As luck would have it, the corridor, in the corridor between two houses were bombed out during the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So there was nobody living there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that corridor was facing smack to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Lisa and Aaron and there-- and my father was standing on one side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was on the outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were shouting in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was shouting in Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CLAPS] Pass the message.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everything's fine, and then-- [CLAPS] And off I went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was Tuesday.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was also lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was Tuesday.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a market day, so was a lot of farmers in the city there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was full, so I got lost in the, in the crowd.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I went to a postage store, bought some stamps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I bought a cross, and I bought a prayer book, a Catholic prayer book in Polish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was just killing time, to just stay and now to go to sleep maybe later on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as I walk, just killing time, suddenly a little girl goes up to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
